<p class="font-display-lg text-headline-md md:text-headline-lg text-primary leading-tight font-bold italic">
                        "To empower the next generation of global businesses by architecting software that is as reliable as it is revolutionary."
                    </p>
</div>
<div class="w-full md:w-1/2 relative group">
<div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary rounded-xl blur opacity-25 group-hover:opacity-50 transition duration-1000 group-hover:duration-200"></div>
