<!-- Section 4: Core Values (Bento Grid Style) -->
<section class="py-xl px-md max-w-container-max mx-auto">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-white mb-xl text-center">Core Engineering Principles</h2>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-gutter">
<!-- Precision -->
<div class="glass-card p-lg rounded-xl md:col-span-2 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-5xl mb-md" data-icon="target">target</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-white mb-sm">Precision</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">We don't just write code; we architect systems with micron-level attention to detail, ensuring zero-latency performance and unbreakable stability.</p>
</div>
<!-- Innovation -->
<div class="glass-card p-lg rounded-xl md:col-span-2 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary text-5xl mb-md" data-icon="rocket_launch">rocket_launch</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-white mb-sm">Innovation</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Stagnation is the enemy. We constantly integrate cutting-edge frameworks and experimental technologies to stay three steps ahead of the curve.</p>
</div>
<!-- Collaboration -->
<div class="glass-card p-lg rounded-xl md:col-span-2 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary text-5xl mb-md" data-icon="hub">hub</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-white mb-sm">Collaboration</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">We operate as an extension of your team. Our radical transparency model ensures you are part of every critical decision and pivot.</p>
</div>
<!-- Integrity -->
<div class="glass-card p-lg rounded-xl md:col-span-2 group hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-primary-container text-5xl mb-md" data-icon="verified_user">verified_user</span>
<h3 class="font-headline-md text-headline-md text-white mb-sm">Integrity</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">We build with ethics in mind. Security, privacy, and long-term maintainability are baked into every line of code we ship.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Section 5: Team -->
